name: Dinari ITA
description: The Dinari ITA dShares token (ITA.d) represents 1:1 ownership of shares in the iShares U.S. Aerospace & Defense ETF (NYSE Arca: ITA). This exchange-traded fund seeks to track the investment results of an index composed of U.S. equities in the aerospace and defense sector. Each ITA.d token is fully backed by a corresponding ITA ETF share, securely held in a transparent and auditable treasury. By leveraging blockchain technology, ITA.d provides investors with exposure to the aerospace and defense industries through a regulated financial product, offering benefits such as 24/7 trading, fractional ownership, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
